  (gr_text "Limit: 0V-35V (polarized)\nLimit (<10µF): –50V-+50V" (at 17.78 39.37 180) (layer "B.SilkS") (tstamp 1707a8c6-4e35-4d59-b7d6-ecc00b6e8ce5)
